          <button>Book an appointment</button>
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="insured" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="insured">
          <p>Circle Bath treats patients with private medical insurance. If you have insurance, Circle Bath will invoice the insurance company for any procedures, tests and diagnostics carried out. There may be certain items not covered by your insurance company, such as private prescriptions, so you should always contact your insurer regarding their ‘excess payment policy' to check your level of cover. For items not covered under the insurance, the team at Circle Bath will contact you to discuss payment directly.</p>
          <button>Book an appointment</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
